{
  "stem": "11998.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she was the pride and joy of my family, really.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she learned French and Latin.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, as a matter of fact, during the war years, when we didn't go to school, she was the one that took in kids to teach in order to make some money.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was one of her students in her class.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I benefited from her brilliance.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She was very kind.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were very good friends.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The only time she didn't want me around was when she went out with boys.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And other than that, the typical sibling situation.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We fought.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had our fights, but we also had our good times together.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I used to-- I used to like to watch my mother cook.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was an excellent cook.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I used to help her in the kitchen, make challah and fish, gefilte fish, and carp.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she was an excellent baker, and she always used to let me help her bake.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So it was the normal-- normal dishes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Potato salad was a specialty, with salami, and eggs, and cakes, and, you know, all of the things that everybody likes.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Nobody likes flanken.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I didn't like flanken.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] We like chicken, and we didn't like porridge, and we didn't like [NON-ENGLISH] which is [NON-ENGLISH] or cereals.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And so that's-- you know, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I had not a very wealthy background, but it was a very warm and very loving background.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my fondest memories, I think, is usually Pesach.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Pesach was-- the-- the time just before Pesach, we used to get new shoes, and new clothes, and get special gifts.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So that was-- that was the-- the time that we really, really enjoyed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a very, very important holiday.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
